org.modelio.vbasic.auth

Interface IAuthData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AuthData, NetAuthData, NoneAuthData, UnknownAuthData, UserPasswordAuthData

    public interface IAuthData
    Interface for authentication data used to connect to remote locations.

    Implementations should sub class the abstract AuthData class.
